uit/more/number/images/img_number_05-sp.jpg\" alt=\"月平均残業時間 10時間15分／月\" class=\"only-sp\">\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"large\">\r\n<img src=\"/wp/wp-content/themes/gyosei_co/images/v/recruit/more/number/images/img_number_06.jpg\" alt=\"平均勤続年数 22.3年 男性22.6年 女性21.9年\" class=\"only-pc\">\r\n<img src=\"/wp/wp-content/themes/gyosei_co/images/v/recruit/more/number/images/img_number_06-sp.jpg\" alt=\"平均勤続年数 22.3年 男性22.6年 女性21.9年\" class=\"only-sp\">\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wdt940\">\r\n\r\n<article class=\"articleBox\">\r\n<div class=\"btnPanel btm_navi\">\r\n<ul class=\"wdt780\">\r\n<li>\r\n<a href=\"/recruit/more/training/\" class=\"on\"><img src=\"/wp/wp-content/themes/gyosei_co/images/v/recruit/more/images/img_more_bnr-training.jpg\" alt=\"training 教育・研修\"></a>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<a href=\"/recruit/more/welfare/\" class=\"on\"><img src=\"/wp/wp-content/themes/gyosei_co/images/v/recruit/more/images/img_more_bnr-welfare.jpg\" alt=\"benefits 福利厚生\"></a>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</article>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- END mainContents --></section>\r\n\r\n<!-- END content --></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<nav id=\"sideNavi\" class=\"sideNavi_recruit\">\r\n<div class=\"categoryLabel only-sp\">採用情報</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"only-pc\"><a href=\"/recruit/president/rec_message/\"><span>社長メッセージ</span></a></li>\r\n<li class=\"only-sp\"><a href=\"/recruit/president/rec_message/\"><span>社長からのメッセージ</span></a></li>\r\n<li class=\"only-sp\"><a href=\"/recruit/president/rec_history/\"><span>沿革</span></a></li>\r\n<li class=\"only-sp\"><a href=\"/recruit/president/rec_outline/\"><span>会社概要</span></a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"/recruit/rec_business/\"><span>お客様のニーズと当社の事業</span></a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"/recruit/interview/\"><span>社員インタビュー</span></a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"/recruit/more/\" class=\"current\"><span>ぎょうせいのここが知りたい！</span></a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"/recruit/rec_contact/\"><span>採用に関するお問い合わせ</span></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"backList